{"tid":2064962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［衝出嚟 撐強仔？！］國統局:6億人月入千元可從全國數據印證","createTime":"2020-06-15T07:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T08:20:08.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a7083e666fad9cc03848c24290bcf0aaead4a889","tid":2064962,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯國家統計局新聞發言人付凌暉表示，有關數據來源可以從全國住戶收支與生活狀況調查數據得到印證。<br />\n<br />\n⋯根據2019年相關數據，低收入組和中間偏下收入組共40%家庭戶，人口6.1億人，年人均收入為11485元，每月人均收入近1000元。其中，低收入組戶月人均收入低於1000元，中間偏下收入組戶月人均收入高於1000元。<br />\n<br />\n付凌暉指出，這些數據反映了內地社會主要矛盾，是人民日益增長的美好生活需要和不平衡不充分展之間的矛盾，反映了基本國情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2494535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2494535&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8re6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=550a0c55\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2494535</a>"},{"pid":"8d40a4c0ea72b3c4a2fc9ee47a4732122d661db4","tid":2064962,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614dcd1e638a7d47721d56a3605fc43d438feff2","tid":2064962,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832987a7abd13a6be717b89e5f62218e04444941","tid":2064962,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"果隻小學雞連加減乘除都未搞得掂識鳩呢啲統計學概念咩 同佢講呢啲根本就係「對熊彈琴」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}